==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*ἀγαθός / agathos / ag-ath-os'

===Etymology===
*A primary word; “good” (in any sense, often as noun): 

===Noun===
'''ἀγαθός'''

# [[benefit]], [[good]] (-s, things), [[well]]. Compare G2570.

